                    <section id="abstract">
                        <h2>Abstract</h2>
                        <div datatype="rdf:HTML" property="schema:abstract">
                            <p>This article presents <em>sparqlines</em>: statistical observations fetched from SPARQL endpoints and displayed as inline-charts. An inline-chart, also known as a <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sparkline"><em>sparkline</em></a>, is concise, and located where it is discussed in the text, complementing the supporting text without breaking the reader’s flow. For example, the 
